.cs 3 on
.cs 2 on
.cm 'Page Mode UDLR' 'Updated on 12/15/83 by JDN'
You can move the cursor around the screen by using the four arrow keys on most
terminals.  However, if your terminal does not have arrow keys you can use the
the control character alternates.

                         *------*
                         |CTRL-U|
               *------*  *------*  *------*
               |CTRL-L|            |CTRL-R|
               *------*  *------*  *------*
                         |CTRL-D|
                         *------*
.cs 2 off
.cs 3 off
